(5, 1, 3, 'Laptops', 'The latest Intel processor, a bigger hard drive, plenty of memory, and even more new features all fit inside just one liberating inch. The new Mac laptops have the performance, power, and connectivity of a desktop computer. Without the desk part.', 'laptops', 'Apple laptops', 'Apple MacBook Air-Laptops', 'Powerful and chic Apple laptops'),
